{"tid":2289044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安心App窺用家相片　檔案　 索大量權限　IT專家：不符比例","createTime":"2020-11-17T03:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T15:09:53.000Z","uid":137088,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"54741593fcd3ecfde5c71c3cf1f606fdd456b5eb","tid":2289044,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】政府昨推出「安心出行」感染風險通知流動應用程式，但當中涉及的私隱問題一直惹人關注，就在流動應用程式推出首天，有網民及資訊科技界人士發現程式的Android版本要求大量權限，包括容許讀取用家手機內相片及媒體內容、檢視網絡連線等。數據科學家黃浩華質疑，為何「安心出行」功能不算多，但卻要求用家交出不成比例的權限，更提醒用戶要留意讀取相片或Wi-Fi權限要求，保障私隱風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/WLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FWLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4wKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=3a3ee6d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FWLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4%2F&h=058bf0cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/WLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4/</a>"},{"pid":"50cf4a3f057db7997fbf1ea6a2fe13420a5f0fff","tid":2289044,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e901768d910a52e06a738119c70af1d1c2f3622b","tid":2289044,"uid":5490,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"裝嗰個都on9"},{"pid":"f341aa426dbd78b6d9aed206e73f7590ac497f56","tid":2289044,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"香港人有撚私隱咩, 私隱係黑警高官先有架"},{"pid":"d7074950942b20805de1b3605681d4681bb13618","tid":2289044,"uid":223198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e901768d910a52e06a738119c70af1d1c2f3622b","tid":2289044,"uid":5490,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"裝嗰個都on9"},"citedBy":